{"tid":1511063,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 在日台妹同我地講奸爸爹","createTime":"2019-08-27T11:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T00:43:25.000Z","uid":54719,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b23212ffabab11b3c0141dbb304a3fd6039c3701","tid":1511063,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:53:40.000Z","msg":"今次去京都book咗間民宿，<br />\n離京阪鐵路十分鐘路程，<br />\n本身就算拎住行李都算近，無乜嘢<br />\n不過今日衰在落大雨，<br />\n一手拎摭一手拎行李，<br />\n一抽二lung搞左好耐先搵到間野喺邊。<br />\n入到去循例都要交低passport畀人mark低，我交到佢手先認真望個host個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好&middot;鬼&middot;靚</span></span><br />\n本身我哋係用英文溝通既，但佢見到我passport後就問我識唔識講Mandarin，<br />\n之後就用國語對話。<br />\n內容講咩就唔好公開好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係總之，最後佢用力得黎又有少少唔好意思咁用雙手緊握做咗個加油既手勢，仲叫我喺連登幫佢同大家打氣咁話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報告完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377ec418532dc783d87deb0df60af02ad2815c25","tid":1511063,"uid":130174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"0b05f0bf691cb8d654d1b2e41c8026742a74b403","tid":1511063,"uid":54719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i50fv7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi50fv7Z.jpg&h=b4ca4738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNKzMGj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNKzMGj.jpg&h=fdbe1e8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc2dd2c42ac8162596900e94592182868033745f","tid":1511063,"uid":20845